Rider :
    - riderId
    - riderName
    - riderStatus
    - getters and setters
ISubscriber :
    -notifyRideRequest()
Driver implements the interface:
    - driver Id
    - driverStatus
    - vehicle details
    - getters and setters
    - notifyRideRequest()
Request :
    - riderId
    - driverId - default - null
    - requestStatus
    - startLocation
    - endLocation
    - getters and setters for riderId and driverId location attributes.
    - synchronised updateRequest()
RequestRepo :
    - Map<requestId, Request>
    - getRequest(requestId)
    - addRequest(requestId)
RiderRepo :
    - Map<riderId, Rider>
    - getRider()
    - addRider()
DriverRepo :
    - Map<driverId, Driver>
    - getDriver()
    - addDriver()
Matching Strategy :
    - match(Request)
MatchingStrategyImplementations :
    - DriverRepo
    - LocationService
    - match(Request)
    - sortByLocation()
BookingService :
    - matchingStrategy
    - driverRepo
    - riderRepo
    - requestRepo
    - acceptRequest(requestId, driverId)
    - createRequest(riderId, startPoint, endPoint)
    - cancelRequest(requestId)
Orchestrator :
    - bookingService
    - createRideRequest(riderId, startPoint, endPoint)
    - acceptRideRequest(requestId, driverId)
    - cancelRequest(requestId)

